            <div class="title">
                Maximum National Effort
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1941-12-02/debates/fd973012-773d-4419-b0ca-4fbac0e4fce5/ExpiringLawsContinuanceBill" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
