            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-6d9b0ef9-7184-4c57-a75b-0c818450739e">
                Mr. Bellenger  (Bassetlaw)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-6d9b0ef9-7184-4c57-a75b-0c818450739e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
