<p class="">And ownership, but I am urging this extension now not as a piece of Socialist theory. I believe that theory is sound and I am prepared to argue it when <span id="1045" class="column-number" data-column-number="1045"></span> the time is suitable, but this is not the time for theorising. [<em>Interruption.</em>] I listened to the hon. Member for Shettleston (Mr. McGovern) the other day for over an hour, and I hope he will have the goodness to listen to me.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
