<p class="">My reading of it was the other way.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-445c750d-3e75-4bde-a8b2-ee855cd722f1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
