<p class="">Was the employer of the young man paid on a cost-plus basis?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-c62a54fe-456a-4cb4-86c4-53a209a29fef" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
